<p align="center">
<font color="#006400" size="+2"><a name="bio">Biographical</a></font>
</p>

<blockquote>
<table>
<tr>
    <td>Name:</td>    
    <td>Harry MATHEWS</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Nationality:</td>
    <td>USA</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Born:</td>    
    <td>14 February 1930</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Awards:</td>
    <td><font size="-1">NEA grant in fiction writing, 1982</font></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td></td>
    <td><font size="-1">National Academy and Institute of Arts and Letters<br>fiction writing award, 1991</font></td>
</tr>
</table>
<br>

<font size="-1">
<ul>
	<li>Attended Princeton, graduated from Harvard (in music)
	<li>Only American member of the Oulipo
	<li><i>Tlooth</i> and <i>The Sinking of the Odradek Stadium</i> translated into French by Georges Perec
</ul>
</font>

</blockquote>

