	<li><i>Immeasurable Distances</i> - <font size="-1">criticism, 1991</font>
	<li><i>The Journalist</i> - <font size="-1">novel, 1994</font>
	<li><a href="/reviews/mathewsh/hcountry.htm">The Human Country</a> - <font size="-1">stories, 2002</font>
	<li><i>The Case of the Persevering Maltese</i> - <font size="-1">non-fiction, 2003</font>
	<li><a href="/reviews/mathewsh/mycia.htm">My Life In CIA</a> - <font size="-1">memoir, 2005</font>
</ul>

<font size="-1">
<p align="center">
Please note that this bibliography is not necessarily complete.<br>
Dates given are of first publication.
</p>
</font>

</blockquote>

